### Add intervenor to occurrence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence/1/intervenors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervenorId": 1
}

### Remove intervenor from occurrence
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence/1/intervenors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervenorId": 1
}

### Update Intervenor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/intervenor/update/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

{
    "name": "Teste Atualizado"
}

### Create Evidence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evidence
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="Evidencia1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< C:\Users\josec\Downloads\Evidencia1.png
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": { "category": "photo", "severity": "high" },
  "location": "Lisbon",
  "description": "Fire evidence image",
  "reporterId": 1,
  "occurrenceId": 1
}
--boundary123--

### SSE for Evidence
GET http://localhost:8080/api/evidence/1/listen
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

### Delete Evidence
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/evidence/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

### Create Report
POST http://localhost:8080/api/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creatorId": 1,
  "title": "Fire Report",
  "description": "Detailed report of the fire incident.",
  "occurrenceId": 1,
  "addons": {
    "photos": [1],
    "documents": [1]
  },
  "language": "pt"
}

### SSE for Report
GET http://localhost:8080/api/report/1/listen
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

